      Cantrips (at will) [mage hand](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/mage-hand), [minor illusion](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/minor-illusion), [ray of frost](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/ray-of-frost)    
