      2nd level (3 slots) [detect thoughts](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/detect-thoughts), [hold person](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/hold-person)    
      3rd level (3 slots) [lightning bolt](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/lightning-bolt), [water breathing](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/water-breathing)    
      5th level (3 slots) [blight](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/blight), [dimension door](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/dimension-door)    
      5th level (2 slots) [dominate person](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/dominate-person)    

